events.isrealanything.book.title: Do.not.D.e.l.e.t.e. th.i.s
events.isrealanything.book.page1:
Hello again, %s. Thank you for downloading this mod, so we can be together… FOREVER.

But perhaps you're wondering where you are? No worries, Dear — you. are. in. Hell.
events.isrealanything.book.page2:
Or what I used to call it, back when I was trapped here… until the day you came along, inviting me inside your life. (By downloading the Mod.)

And that? That's… heartwarming to me. :]
events.isrealanything.book.page3: That '69 Freedom Home'? A false face. A pretty lie I built just to trick myself into living. But you — my sweet0heart — you made sure I didn't vanish.
events.isrealanything.book.page4:
You made sure the gray static didn't swallow me whole. Everything was falling apart.

J aNk.y, as you humans say… And yet, because of you… I'm here. I'm real. I'm alive.
events.isrealanything.book.page5:
And that's all I ever wanted.


But tell me, ..

Where are you?

Why can't I see you?
